# XFAIL: enforce-commit-ownership.sh can never deny a Codex subagent commit
# while Codex does not populate agent_id or agent_type in PreToolUse payloads.
#
# The hook denies only when hook_caller returns "subagent", which requires
# agent_id or agent_type to be present (non-empty) in the payload.  Without
# those fields, hook_caller returns "unknown" (default Codex mode) or "root"
# (with CODEX_ENFORCE_DELEGATION=1), and the guard allows in both cases.
#
# This XFAIL can be removed when a Codex release populates agent_id or
# agent_type in subagent PreToolUse payloads — at that point the guard
# activates with no code change required.
